profile_positions.description:
Managed a team of 35 Sales & Services specialists including (Product) Marketing professionals.  
# Restructured the Datahotel offering (from a loss leader back to profitability) to one of the most successful Managed Services portfolio items; 
# Product Management (P&L responsible) and Product Development (ROI responsible), strategic competitive positioning and new business development (revenue responsible);
# Rebuild activities of KPN's technical Cybercenter facilities.

# Developed from scratch on a new Dedicated Housing & Hosting services portfolio;
# Business development for all Hosting & Housing services (shared, dedicated, custom hosting; co-location; cybercenter services);
# Advertising concept development; Competition, Industry and Customer Satisfaction research.

Building a relationship network with affinity groups, customer advisory councils and organizations for professionals in the Netherlands (a.o. GVB Amsterdam; Chipper; Horeca Nederland;.Binnenvaart Nederland);  
# Extensive field contacts and marketing research to strategically identify and prioritize new service/business opportunities using Intermediary Marketing;  
# External and internal customer relationship management, multi-project management, and sales channel/partner development.

# Restructuring and rebuilding "hands-on" marketing in the largest market area of the Netherlands; 
# Drove loyalty marketing programs, new business development, consumer retail marketing, SME and corporate relationship management functions;  
# Competitive positioning, market research, marketing communications, infrastructure planning & investments, product trails, shop research, implementation of defined marketing programs including direct sales support and quality assurance.

# Manager Strategy and Positioning for the Dutch computer branch;
# Market Research manager for telephony and computer industry; 
# Responsible for Product Management and market introduction (all P's) of the first (non-proprietary) product range of minicomputers in the Netherlands.

# Project Manager International Market Research, involved with large-scale behavioural research in Europe (smoking habits panel) and advertising concept-testing on behalf of Turmac's internal advertising agency;   
# Project Manager Marketing Information Systems manager of a multi-functional IT Development team defined and realized new sales and marketing information systems in a number of European countries;  
# Manager of the European PC support group;
# EU Marketing, advertising and panel research; 
# Restructured, redesigned and built the business intelligence department.
